title: UFO Sightings & More with the late UFO Researcher Timothy Beckley
description:
The late UFO researcher Timothy Beckley sat down to discuss historically UFO sightings and much more during this interview conducted in 2017. He was an amazing human being who dedicated his life to research into extraterrestrial intelligences and more. Timothy, may you rest in a beautiful and everlasting peace. Get all his books for your collection on Amazon.
